curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/12628' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM2077B", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM2077B is an ultra-high PSRR, fast transient  response, low noise and low dropout voltage linear  regulator which is designed using CMOS technology. It  provides 1.5A output current capability. The operating  input voltage range is from 0.5V to 5.5V and bias  supply voltage range is from 2.5V to 5.5V. The  adjustable output voltage range is from 0.5V to 3.3V.  Other features include 1.2V logic-controlled shutdown  mode, short-circuit current limit and thermal shutdown  protection. The SGM2077B has automatic discharge  function to quickly discharge VOUT in the disabled status.  The  SGM2077B  is  available  in  a  Green  WLCSP-0.8×1.2-6B-B package. It operates over an  operating temperature range of -40℃ to +125℃.    "}'
